display="inline"><![CDATA[N\geqslant \nu ]]></fr:tex>, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[U_N]]></fr:tex> be the open subset of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> consisting of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s\in  S]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {rank}_{k(s)}M_{ns}\otimes _{\mathcal {O}_{S,s}} k(s)\leqslant  P(n)]]></fr:tex> for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\nu \leqslant  n\leqslant  N]]></fr:tex>.
    Then the decreasing sequence of open subsets <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[U_N]]></fr:tex> stabilises.</fr:p>
  
    
